---
import Bi from '../shared/Bi.astro';
import Callout from '../shared/Callout.astro';
import Section from '../mechanics/Section.astro';
---
<Section id="server-types" titleZh="先選對伺服器" titleEn="Pick the right server first" eyebrow="Before Day 1">
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="Travian 同時開很多種伺服器，每種速度與規則不同。官方速度可從 1x 到 10x（x10 約 35 天結算），新手建議從標準 1x 速度練起，熟練後再嘗試快速或年度特別版。"
      en="Travian runs several server types in parallel, with different speeds (1x to 10x — x10 finishes in ~35 days) and rule sets. Beginners should start on standard 1x; once comfortable, try faster servers or annual specials."
    />
  </p>

  <table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: var(--space-4) 0; font-size: var(--fs-sm);">
    <thead>
      <tr style="background:var(--bg-2); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-0);">
        <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;"><Bi zh="伺服器類型" en="Server type" /></th>
        <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;"><Bi zh="速度" en="Speed" /></th>
        <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;"><Bi zh="長度" en="Length" /></th>
        <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;"><Bi zh="特色" en="Highlights" /></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="標準 (Standard)" en="Standard" /></td><td style="padding:8px;">1x</td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="約 250 天" en="~250 days" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="入門首選；Lumi 指南預設場景" en="Beginner default; the scenario the Lumi guide is written for" /></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="速度 (Speed)" en="Speed" /></td><td style="padding:8px;">3x / 5x</td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="約 80–150 天" en="~80–150 days" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="所有時間 / 訓練 / 移動 ÷ 速度倍率；要更高活躍度" en="All times / training / travel ÷ speed; demands higher activity" /></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="競技賽 (Tournament)" en="Tournament" /></td><td style="padding:8px;">3x / 5x</td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="約 100 天" en="~100 days" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="高手競技；Final 進入官方總決賽" en="Competitive; finalists qualify for official championship" /></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="年度特別版 (Annual Special)" en="Annual Special" /></td><td style="padding:8px;">1x / 2x</td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="約 250 天" en="~250 days" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="每年 9 月開服；加入新族與機制（過去：Fire & Sand 埃及人/匈、Glory of Sparta 斯巴達人、Northern Legends 維京人、Path to Pandora 系統大改）" en="Launched every September; adds new tribes / mechanics (past: Fire & Sand for Egyptians/Huns, Glory of Sparta, Northern Legends for Vikings, Path to Pandora system overhaul)" /></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="新年特別版 (New Year Special)" en="New Year Special" /></td><td style="padding:8px;">1x / 2x</td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="約 250 天" en="~250 days" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="每年 1 月開服；綜合過去特別版機制" en="Launched every January; combines features from past specials" /></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="Community Week" en="Community Week" /></td><td style="padding:8px;">varies</td><td style="padding:8px;">varies</td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="實驗性伺服器，玩家投票選規則" en="Experimental; features chosen by community vote" /></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="地區特別服 (Local)" en="Local Gameworlds" /></td><td style="padding:8px;">varies</td><td style="padding:8px;">varies</td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="特定社群限定（如 TW、HK、JP），有地區徽章與在地化功能" en="Community-restricted (e.g., TW, HK, JP); medals + localized features" /></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-0);"><Bi zh="測試版 (Beta / PTR)" en="Beta / PTR" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="不固定" en="varies" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="不固定" en="varies" /></td><td style="padding:8px;"><Bi zh="測試新功能，常常重置；不適合認真打" en="Tests new features; frequent resets; not for serious play" /></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <Callout kind="warn" titleZh="速度伺服器的陷阱" titleEn="Speed server pitfalls">
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="3x 速度看起來只是「3 倍快」但實際上：(1) 你睡 8 小時 = 別人遊戲內 24 小時，sitter 是必需而非可選；(2) Op 時間會壓縮到 30 天內就開打，沒有時間慢慢摸索；(3) 金幣優勢被放大（5 分鐘 instant build 變相省更多時間）。新手別跳速度。"
        en="3x speed looks like '3× faster' but in reality: (1) your 8h sleep = 24h in-game, sitters become mandatory not optional; (2) the first OP often happens by Day 30, no time to learn; (3) gold's value compounds (5-minute instant builds save proportionally more)."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>
</Section>
